Happy 10th Anniversary, ‘KUWTK!’ The 15 Most Viral Kardashian GIFs of All Time (PHOTOS)

Can you believe today, October 14, marks the tenth anniversary of Keeping Up With The Kardashians?!

Yup, we've been following this out-there family's wild antics for an entire decade now, and we are baffled at how famous they still are quickly time has flown by.

To celebrate this momentous pop culture milestone, we're looking back at the legendary show's most popular GIFs of all time, from Khloe's contagious laugh to, of course, Kim's unforgettable cry face.

Take a stroll down memory lane in the slides above, courtesy of Gfycat!

Keeping Up With The Kardashians airs Sundays at 9 p.m. ET on E!.
